Hey!

I have a problem with checkbox lists in forms.
The problem is that every checkbox in the field name is prefixed with _0-2/_

This means that it is not possible to autopopulate fields in the form with the internal property name from the url.

Is there any reason that it's prefixd with _0-2/_?
